● 13/13 — all green. Here's what was confirmed end-to-end against live Sepolia:

  Phase 1 — Crypto (offline)
  - Keygen, encrypt/decrypt with BALANCE_SCALE, homomorphic add, homomorphic sub, wrong-key rejection

  Phase 2 — Contract (live Sepolia)
  - is_registered → register → tx confirmed
  - get_encrypted_balance → decrypt → 0 STRK ✓
  - approve + deposit 0.01 STRK → tx confirmed → decrypt on-chain balance → 0.01 STRK ✓
  - withdraw 0.005 STRK → tx confirmed → decrypt on-chain balance → 0.005 STRK ✓

  Also updated constants.ts to point at the clean 0x7481... contract (the same one the test just exercised).



 

